<head>ABANDON</head>
<div type="definition">

    <p resp="#chris" modified="2021-03-19T14:24:09.507+09:00">DISCARD SOMEONE WHOM ONE SHOULD CARE FOR.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
        <div type="old-chinese-criteria" resp="#CH" modified="2022-07-20T18:53:14.082+09:00">
